COMMUNITY EDITION SCOPE

This MIT License applies to the following components of AX-TrafficAnalyzer:

INCLUDED FEATURES:
- WiFi hotspot creation and management (hostapd + dnsmasq)
- Transparent HTTPS MITM interception
- Traffic capture and logging
- Basic protocol analysis (HTTP, TLS, DNS)
- PCAP export for Wireshark integration
- Web dashboard (basic traffic viewing)
- REST API (core endpoints)
- WebSocket server (real-time updates)
- Session and device tracking
- Basic vulnerability scanning (passive only)
- Plugin system (core framework)
- IPv6 dual-stack support
- Certificate management with automatic rotation
- Time synchronization (NTP integration)
- GDPR compliance tools
- Disk space management
- Network partition resilience
- Atomic startup orchestration

THIRD-PARTY DEPENDENCIES:
All MIT-licensed dependencies remain under their original licenses.
See NOTICES.md for complete attributions.

ENTERPRISE FEATURES:
For Enterprise Edition features (ML, active scanning, fuzzing, etc.),
see LICENSE-ENTERPRISE. Enterprise features are NOT covered by this
MIT License and require a separate commercial license.

